	  the \csname, in case there are macros; foreign accents, for example.
	Bug report from Dumas Patrice <dumas@centre-cired.fr>.

	* makeinfo/makeinfo.c (COMMAND_CHAR): new macro, and exclude ^ and
	_ from command names.
	(read_token): call it.

