	From: "Andreas Herrmann" <AHERRMAN@de.ibm.com>.

	* lib/Makefile.am (libtxi_a_SOURCES): include xalloc.h.

	* doc/Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): skip macro.texi and userdoc.texi now.
	(common_mandeps): new var.
