	* doc/texinfo.txi: mention pdfcolor.tex.
	* doc/texinfo.tex: doc.
	* doc/Makefile.am (install-tex): install pdfcolor.tex too.
	* doc/pdfcolor.tex: new file, since Kurt.Hornik@ci.tuwien.ac.at
		reports that not all pdftex installations include it.

