2000-11-10    <karl@gnu.org>

	* dir-example: update
	* info/nodes.c: doc fixes, etc.

	* incorporated verbatim patch from janneke:
    2000-04-14    <janneke@gnu.org>

	    * applied texinfo-3.12s.jcn4 patch

    1999-09-02    <janneke@gnu.org>

	    * makeinfo/cmds.c,
