    1999-09-01    <janneke@gnu.org>

	    * makeinfo/makeinfo.c: bf: @exdent (urg6.texi) -- Rolled into 4.0
	    * NEWS: added verb* to Language section
	    * doc/texinfo.txi: @verb, @verbatim doco
