	    used if bibentries reference other bibentries.  Moreover, looking
	    for `Citation' in the LOG should be enough to avoid uneless runs.

  Sun Mar  7 15:15:00 1999 UTC Karl Heinz Marbaise <kama@hippo.fido.de>

