	* util/texi2dvi: Add --pdf.

	* util/texi2dvi: New option -@ to use @input and @nonstopmode, in
		case texinfo is preloaded.
	From: Khimenko Victor <khim@sch57.msk.ru>
	Date: Sun, 20 Dec 1998 02:04:12 +0300 (EET)

