        arrow keys work:
	* info/infomap.c: Add arrow key bindings.
        (keymap_bind_keyseq): New support function.
	(initialize_info_keymaps): Use it.
	(term_ku,term_kd,term_kl,term_kr): Remove explicit declarations;
	use #include "terminal.h" instead.
